  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is buffet style with lots of options like freshly baked cakes, croissants, jams,<span> </span>locally produced<span> </span>honey, as well as other local products. </p>
<p>If you choose to upgrade to half board<span> you'll get to try some exceptional food - excellent appetizers, fresh fish and tasty pasta dishes - every single evening.</span></p>
<p><strong>Restaurant</strong></p>
<p>The chef uses fresh local ingredients, served up in a beautiful setting beside the pool. So all you'll need to do is relax and enjoy - the toughest part is deciding which wine to have with your meal, they have a fantastic selection. </p>
<p><strong>Bistro Bar</strong></p>
<p>The bistro bar is open from morning to evening. You'll be able to grab quick snacks from here, enjoy light lunches from the grill. It's the best spot for cocktails at sunset too.</p>
<p><strong>The Winery </strong></p>
<p>They have wide selection of wines and champagne on offer. Just speak to your waiter who will be able to offer you advice on the best options to suit your tastes or accompany your meal.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
