  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Come to Hotel Costa Dei Fiori to take a break from your usual routine. Relax beside the pool, with views of the sea. Get a feel for authentic <a data-udi="umb://document/c7d9c305cd1e44568dec1178157bc9f9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c7d9c305cd1e44568dec1178157bc9f9}" title="Sardinia">Sardinia</a>, staying in rooms in the traditional villas dotted about the beautiful park gardens, filled with palm trees. You'll be right on the coast - so you can easily reach some of Sardinia's pristine sandy beaches. </p>]]></listingDescription>
