  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms </strong>are located in the park gardens, in small typical Sardinian villas, surrounded by plants and flowers. With cool tiled floors, decorated in blues and whites and local artisanal furniture throughout, the rooms have a distinctly Mediterranean feel. These rooms sleep up to two people and have views of the park or pool. Facilities include air conditioning, a digital safe, TV, mini-bar, telephone and a hairdryer. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are more spacious and comfortable. They have large panoramic windows and a private patio or terrace that overlook the the gardens. These rooms sleep up to three people. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
